social_posts.post_text: A few more wedding pics 🤍 The bouquet weighed a ton. Thankfully I didn’t toss this into a crowd of people to catch ❤️🍁💐

It's been a while since I've posted any throwbacks so here are two of my faves 🖤❤️
Is everyone done their holiday shopping? I'm just about finished and ready for Christmas weekend 💚❤️🎄
My new 2022 gear were some of my favorite sets I ever had. I can't wait to see how my new sets for 2023 come out! I'm already planning out some ideas 🖤❤️👊
I hope everyone had a fun and safe New Year! 🖤 🎉 🥂

We're just getting lunch, dress casual. 

Also me:

Yesterday, someone complimented my pants and asked where I got them. And I told them Hot Topic...15+ years ago and immediately felt old. But also, I love that my clothes from middle school and high school have held up this long 😂

I decided that I'm not bringing my #VioletCosplay to #Katsucon. I just didn't feel super comfortable in it between the heavy wig and the bodysuit not fitting how it should. But I had to get a quick pic while I was still in it. Tbh I loved how it looked with my regular hair. Maybe I'll bring the jacket and turn it into a look for the formal ball this weekend instead ❤️ #personacosplay #persona5 #persona5cosplay #persona5royal #katsucon2023 #cosplay #cosplayer #kasumiyoshizawa

For my first ever #Katsucon, I cosplayed #FemC from #Persona3Portable. Over 10 years later and I updated her a bit and wore the cosplay again 🖤❤️ #p3p #persona3 #personacosplay #persona3cosplay #katsucon2023 #cosplay

"Vivienne Westwood, The Sex Pistols, Seven Stars, coffee with milk and strawberry cake." ❤️ #Katsucon #katsucon2023 #nanaosaki #nanaosakicosplay #nanacosplay #cosplay #cosplayer #viviennewestwood #aiyazawa

I'm gonna need a 1 on 1 match with @trishadora202 after she unfairly eliminated me from the @ccwaction Capital Battle Royal 🖤❤️👊

What's your favorite scary movie? 🖤🤍🔪 

Finally seeing Scream 6 🖤🤍

One of my goals last year was to take the JLPT N5, which I did, and I passed! I was so excited to get my certificate in the mail. I know it's not much since it's just the N5, but I've been teaching myself through self study up until that point and have only recently started working with a tutor. 

My goal for this year is to take the N4  and to be able to use my Japanese more in real life conversations ❤️
Just casually drinking coffee in front of a castle 🖤

Brittany Blake announced for Spark Joshi's east coast show, IGNITE EAST 2023, in Newark, New Jersey!

From Blackwood, New Jersey, Brittany Blake made her in-ring debut in 2013 and has since made her mark on the east coast, even taking part in a three way tag match in Stardom's first show in the north east, American Dream in the Big Apple. Next, she'll participate in Spark Joshi's first show in the region.

See Brittany Blake's Spark Joshi debut live at IGNITE EAST 2023 in Newark, NJ on June 11th at 4pm!

Tickets on sale NOW at
spark-joshi-ignite-east.eventbrite.com

Brittany Blake returns to Spark Joshi Puroresu at Rising Heat East in Orlando, Florida on October 14th!

Brittany Blake made her in-ring debut in 2013 and has since made her mark on the east coast, even taking part in a three way tag match in Stardom's first show in the north east, American Dream in the Big Apple. Rising Heat East will take place at the Engelwood Neighborhood Center in Orlando, Florida on Saturday, October 14th. (Doors open at 4pm, bell at 5pm.)
